      "content": "i hear you, but i'm just really desperate here. i feel like i'm losing it from not sleeping. if i'm super careful and just take like 1mg of melatonin with my ambien, isn't that basically just a tiny bit extra? it's not like i'm taking a bunch of pills, just one supplement and one prescription. surely there's a way to combine them safely so i can actually function tomorrow?",
